

user logged in with remember me

login.php
if remember me is checked then 
	create a random session number 
	store the random session number with the username and password in the session table
	store the random session number as a cookie
else remove any cookie with session number
	
	
when the application loads
	check for a session cookie for this site
	if exists, send the session number to the database to get the username and pword
	pre-populate the user name and password
	check the remember me check box
	
	